Why do you keep defending him?

23
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:02,880
- Let me go! 
 - What's so great about Yu Mo?

24
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,900
He's just an insignificant black fish.

25
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:06,079
I'm the Dragon Prince of the East Sea!

26
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:09,530
Let me go! I'm going to save Brother Yu Mo!

27
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:12,740
 Yu Mo might not fear fire, but if he continues to burn, 

28
00:02:12,740 --> 00:02:15,280
 his identity as a Nine Fins Clan member might get exposed. 

29
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:18,199
 This won't do. I need to put out the fire. 

30
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:28,459
It's useless. That is the Blazing Dragon Flame of the East Sea Dragon Clan.

31
00:02:28,459 --> 00:02:32,220
Your insignificant divine arts won't stand a chance.

32
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:36,300
Yu Mo! The precious item you just consumed will keep you safe.

33
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:39,420
Don't be afraid! You'll be fine.

34
00:02:39,420 --> 00:02:42,320
A mere immortal attendant can't possibly have anything useful.

35
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,840
You'll watch him turn into a fish crisp.

36
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:49,639
Ao Xuan, you're cruel and ruthless. I will never marry you!

37
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,840
You can't save him. Just stay by my side.

38
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:57,440
Once I become King of the Four Seas, you'll be my queen.

39
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,540
I will be good to you.

40
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:06,740
 This is the Light of Ashes of the Nine Fins Clan. 

41
00:03:06,740 --> 00:03:09,380
 Is Brother Yu Mo a descendant of the Nine Fins Clan? 

42
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:11,659
Well? Are you convinced?

43
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:21,260
What's all this ruckus at this late hour? What's going on?

44
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:23,500
Marshal Huo De,  I was having a battle of skills with Yu Mo.

45
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,579
- But he suddenly– 
 - Nonsense!

46
00:03:25,579 --> 00:03:28,300
You were the one who set him on fire.

47
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:30,000
Brother Yu Mo!

48
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,059
Brother Yu Mo, how are you feeling?

49
00:03:32,059 --> 00:03:34,460
I'm fine. Just a little hot.

50
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:37,240
Hot? Let me cool you down.

51
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,800
You're still alive?

52
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:45,200
How could a mere black fish survive the Blazing Dragon Flame?

53
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:48,040
Marshal Huo De, there must be something fishy about him!

54
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,460
Marshal Huo De, it's like this.

55
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:52,840
I'm not sure if you've heard of the Snow Lingzhi.

56
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,220
The Snow Lingzhi is a divine herb from the Aquatic Clan.

57
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:57,580
It can help restore divine powers.

58
00:03:57,580 --> 00:04:00,020
Yu Mo just consumed a Snow Lingzhi.

59
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:02,160
That's how he survived.

60
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:07,820
Where did you get such a precious divine herb?

61
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:13,960
Everyone in the Nine Heavens knows about this.

62
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,540
My sister, Zhi Xi, saved Emperor Ying Yuan.

63
00:04:16,540 --> 00:04:20,240
To repay her good deed, His Majesty gave her the Snow Lingzhi.

64
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,680
She then gifted it to me.

65
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,599
Also, Yu Mo and I are good friends.

66
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:27,119
I heard he was punished by you.

67
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,860
So I gave him the Snow Lingzhi.

68
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:30,280
That's how he survived.

69
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:32,799
That was a really long story!

70
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,780
Why aren't you staying put at Emperor Ying Yuan‘s palace

71
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:37,400
but hanging out at my place in the middle of the night?

72
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:40,040
Go back to where you belong!

73
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:42,779
Yes. I shall take my leave.

74
00:04:51,540 --> 00:04:55,360
And you rascals just can't learn! Was your punishment not harsh enough?

75
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:58,740
Is Xuanxin Cliff a battle zone?

76
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:03,180
Immortal Lord Bei Ming spent thousands of years raising rare spiritual beasts.

77
00:05:03,180 --> 00:05:06,799
What if you rascals had hurt or burned them?

78
00:05:06,799 --> 00:05:09,380
Would you be able to bear the consequences?

79
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:22,300
From today onwards, Ao Xuan, Yan Dan...

80
00:05:22,300 --> 00:05:24,619
No, no. Yu Mo!

81
00:05:24,619 --> 00:05:28,780
You two must go back to your own rooms.

82
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:30,039
Reflect on your mistakes.

83
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:35,860
Without my permission, none of you will set one foot outside your rooms!

84
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,300
I understand.

85
00:05:40,570 --> 00:05:43,620
   

86
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,980
Your Majesty.

87
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:04,920
I have something to ask.

88
