Yan Dan and I are close and we care about each other.

92
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:23,380
I can't bear to see her struggle.

93
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:26,800
Could you send her back to Xuanxin Cliff?

94
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,900
Is this what Yan Dan wants?

95
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,960
A fire broke out at Xuanxin Cliff last night.

96
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,900
In order to save her black fish friend, Yu Mo,

97
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:37,740
Yan Dan gave him the precious Snow Lingzhi.

98
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:41,360
Yan Dan has known Immortal Lord Bei Ming for hundreds of years. They were close.

99
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:44,680
Now she has a confidante in her life.

100
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:47,880
If it were me, I'd wish to go back too.

101
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,640
How generous of her.

102
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,700
You may rise.

103
00:06:57,926 --> 00:06:59,860
If you were the one who sacrificed your heart,

104
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:02,660
why would you ask for grace for someone else?

105
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:04,800
Isn't there anything you want?

106
00:07:05,540 --> 00:07:09,899
I heard Yanxu Heavenly Palace has a divine art called "Flying Strings."

107
00:07:09,899 --> 00:07:12,520
It uses the qin. A very unusual art. 
  (T/N: "Qin" - an ancient stringed instrument) 

108
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,640
I'm very interested in it.

109
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:18,260
I wonder if Your Majesty is willing to teach me.

110
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:12,520
These are the essences of Flying Strings.

111
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,060
Have you memorized it?

112
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,280
Yes.

113
