Back in the Land Under the Horizon, I taught you the Isolation spell.

114
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:37,040
In order to learn the art, you need to get rid of unnecessary thoughts and have a pure heart and mind.

115
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:41,100
Cultivation is about training the heart. Do you understand?

116
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:44,960
 Isolation Spell? Luckily, I learned it before. 

117
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:48,600
Of course, I remember what you taught me.

118
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:52,260
 She's lying to my face and shows no remorse. 

119
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,600
 Punishing Zhi Xi is easy. 

120
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:27,840
 But how should I punish her without hurting Yan Dan? 

121
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,240
 I'll have to think this through. 

122
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:33,200
 His Majesty taught Sister the Isolation Spell. 

123
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,360
 That's right. 

124
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,980
 I thought I was the one in his dreams. 

125
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:50,740
 But he never called out my name in those dreams. 

126
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:55,860
 After all, Ying Yuan is only in love with the one who stayed by his side in the Land Under the Horizon. 

127
00:09:55,860 --> 00:10:02,400
 To him, the wife he grew old with wasn't me, but Zhi Xi. 

128
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:16,020
I'm still injured. My  divine arts are unstable.

129
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:18,160
I'm sorry I startled you, Your Majesty.

130
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:20,560
I'm willing to receive punishment.

